  {
    "user": "U061HDV96",
    "text": "Currently I'm only testing on one device. When I'm ready, which is soon because of the deadline, I'll test it using adb's shell in which you can set the the display size and density: 'adb shell wm display-size' and 'adb shell wm display-density' (change wm to am for Android 4.0-4.2). I've also gotten a couple of testers that'll give some feedback on the devices they have.",
    "ts": "1433690512.000722",
    "id": "07de1069",
    "thread": [
      {
        "position": "null",
        "number": 0
