      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "user": "U053Q5XP2",
    "text": "In my experience, it's only really important to test on a non-nexus pre lollipop device to make sure I got all the theming right in appcompat, considering all the arbitrary attributes you have to duplicate in styles.xml",
    "ts": "1433695303.000725",
    "id": "07de1072",
    "thread": [
      {
        "position": "null",
        "number": 0
      }
    ],
    "label": [
      {
        "type": "null",
        "position": "null"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "user": "U061HDV96",
    "text": "And to test on Samsung devices because of the amount of edge cases you get with those, so I've heard.",
    "ts": "1433695695.000726",
    "id": "07de1073",
    "thread": [
      {
        "position": "null",
        "number": 0
      }
    ],
    "label": [
