  {
    "user": "U061HDV96",
    "text": "<@U04TK850N>: it definitely cannot reflect the real views. But it does give you some more information. It's like Google Chrome's emulator for different devices, it's not perfect, but it comes pretty close imo.",
    "ts": "1433695902.000730",
    "id": "07de1077",
    "thread": [
      {
        "position": "null",
        "number": 0
      }
    ],
    "label": [
